divs: sighting details was outside having a cigarette noticed it was brighter than normal at 9:20pm started looking for source as i looked up it got brighter and brighter noticed a white fireball directly above me shining what i guess to be a spot light\search light at that very second it appeared to shoot strait up i then could make out the outline of a triangle moving to the northwest at a very slow speed watched it go just passed the tree line before i lost site of it .
